item.title: Protein Bars
item.description: This recipe is based (heavily) upon one from none-other than the Doc himself - Greg Doucette. Mike and I have tweaked it slightly (mostly Mike - but he probably won’t read this so I’ll take the credit). This is definitely a good one if you’re planning on eating a lot of protein bars year-round! It is on the pricey side the first time you order all of the ingredients, but if you’re planning on making them they pay for themselves.
